Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥大人…选择我真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是在做梦吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 勇斗大人来视察津利了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥大人来了吗？
