Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:17.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}如同星辰般的海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:21.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}美丽永恒的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:25.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\yshad3}呐喊吧　从此刻起
